channel.title: Server is not getting online
channel.description: I have this problem and I have no clue whats up. I'm almost 100% sure I did everything right, but whenever I go to check if my server is online, it always saids offline. I have no-ip , I portforwarded my router with the port 43594, I have the ipv4 correct, but it seems not to work. I even tried to portforward with UTorrent and it didn't work. So if you have any idea on how to fix this issue, can you please reply or skype me at "lukersps" or even pm me over here. Thank you .
